Title: Establishes a pilot program related to making the gluten content of food available at certain state owned, operated, or leased cafeterias
Summary: Establishes a pilot program related to making the gluten content of food available at certain state owned, operated, or leased cafeterias.
ActClause: AN ACT to establish a pilot program related to making the gluten content of food available at certain state owned, operated, or leased cafeterias; and providing for the repeal of such provisions upon expiration thereof
